      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "The plasmids pPU100 and pPU200 contained the ORF under the control of the T7 promoter and were checked by restriction enzyme digestion and sequencing of the fusion sites using universal T7 primers hybridizing to regions up-and downstream of the insertion site."
